clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺到明你係擤啦"},{"pid":"851062e2158b593cbfb6558f11325fc39cbf1afe","tid":481312,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好慘"},{"pid":"5d7bb55f55b5d098e86143748baa1a170f63371b","tid":481312,"uid":81256,"like":126,"dislike":2,"score":124,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T05:24:56.000Z","msg":"如果係好似廢老果種<br />\n大力噴落地下<br />\n就抵撚死"},{"pid":"44df493c8c4f10309d8b0fd7a70c91b199637389","tid":481312,"uid":155133,"like":100,"dislike":0,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T05:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地捉你擤鼻涕唔係滴喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺到明你係擤啦</blockquote><br />\n咪係 見到啲廢老禁住一個鼻窿<br />\n係咁擤另一個鼻窿啲鼻涕擤到長一長最後吊到落地就想嘔<br />\n<br />\n罰佢$1500算便宜佢"},{"pid":"b48621c107eb9d42b091573902c593ea4cd499fc","tid":481312,"uid":32114,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T05:26:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人地捉你擤鼻涕唔係滴喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺到明你係擤啦</blockquote><br />\n肯定係㩒住一邊鼻窿，另一邊就擤成筒鼻涕嗰種啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常廢中同廢老最鍾意咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a70d2383e60bfb59c932e1746e565fd2bd752d","tid":481312,"uid":32473,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地捉你擤鼻涕唔係滴喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺到明你係擤啦</blockquote><br />\n肯定係㩒住一邊鼻窿，另一邊就擤成筒鼻涕嗰種啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常廢中同廢老最鍾意咁做<img src=\"/asse